This paper focuses on feature selection for cyber attack dataset, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for classification, which suggests that it could also belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of K-nearest neighbor classifier, which falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
